room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Houston Panic Room in Houston
review: I did the phase III human trials room with two other friends. The walkie talkie had a lot of static at first but the operator Jennifer was really good about fixing that asap. Great location and atmosphere. Really recommend to visit.

room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Houston Panic Room in Houston
review: We had a great time here with our organization officer board doing the Human Trials one. Our operator Claudia was great and super friendly! This is my second time doing a panic room here and I will definitely be back for more!

room_title: Escape room "Phase III: Human Trials" by Houston Panic Room in Houston
review: I loved the Phase III: Human Trials, because it was the most challenging one!
